cs.CR, cs.NI, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

The paper discusses security challenges and proposes a new authentication technique for D2D communication in 5G networks. This topic falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and network security (cs.NI). The proposed technique also involves machine learning (cs.AI) for generating user biometric identity. Additionally, the paper mentions the use of accelerometer data (cs.LG) for biometric identification. Finally, the proposed technique has potential applications in mobile multimedia (cs.MM) over 5G networks.
